t: "O believers! Do not waste your charity with reminders ňĻof your generosityňļ or hurtful words, like those who donate their wealth just to show off and do not believe in Allah or the Last Day. Their example is that of a hard barren rock covered with a thin layer of soil hit by a strong rain‚ÄĒleaving it just a bare stone. Such people are unable to preserve the reward of their charity. Allah does not guide ňĻsuchňļ disbelieving people"